```plantuml
@startuml jzyong_GameServer4g

actor Client as C
participant "Gate (Gateway)" as G
participant "Hall Server" as H
participant "World Server" as W
participant "Resource Server" as R
participant "ZooKeeper" as ZK

C -> G: Connect via TCP
G -> ZK: Service registration
G -> H: Connect via gRPC (GameManager)
H -> ZK: Service registration
H -> W: Connect via gRPC (HallManager)
W -> ZK: Service registration
R -> ZK: Service registration

C -> G: Send login request
G -> H: Forward request
H -> W: Authenticate with player data
W -> H: Send authentication result
H -> G: Forward result
G -> C: Send login response

C -> G: Send game action
G -> H: Forward action
H -> W: Process game logic
W -> H: Send game state update
H -> G: Forward update
G -> C: Send game state

@enduml
```